name: LG "LOG" 22
description:
The "Log" was originally prototyped as an art piece but since then it's been sold as end tables, stools and pedestals but ultimately it is a conversation piece. Made from 100% recycled scrap wood the "LOG" is perfect in any environment. They are hand carved from a solid piece of laminated wood end cuts.

SIZE: 12' x 12" x 22"
